The leadership of Niger Delta Campaign For Development And Progressive Governance has endorsed distinguished Senator James Ebiowou Manager as the most preferred candidate for Governor of Delta State come 2023. The Good Governance Group in their endorsement message stated that the action became Paramount and imperative due to the long and in-depth experience Senator James Manager has obtained overtime in his political journey right from the era of former Governor Felix Ibru of blessed memory. Comrade Mike J K Tiemo, the President of the Group who spoke with Daily Independent noted that Senator James Manager had served through the ranks as Bomadi Local Government Chairman, PDP Chairman Delta State, Commissioner for Works, Housing and Transport, before becoming Senator, he can be trusted to govern Delta State in unity love and fairness without bias or any trace of tribalism or segregation. -Advertisement- According to Comrade Mike Tiemo, James Manager is a well-known grassroots politician who is close to the masses as he relates with them without any form of deprivation or impediments, a character trace which has earned the appellation of the man of the people. Comrade Mike Tiemo the Niger Delta Humanitarian Activist remarked that Senator James Manager is indeed a man called for service to humanity, as exemplified by the way he is discharging his social responsibility to the people of Delta South Senatorial District and beyond with the fear of God. Speaking further he added: “Distinguished Senator Ebiowou Manager has the requisite knowledge and the political sagaçity to navigate the murky Political Waters and carry on the reins of government and take Delta State to greater heights like London and Singapore after the era of Governor Okowa when he becomes Governor. Comrade Tiemo Who emphasized the need for Deltans particularly the delegates to support James Manager in the Delta State Governorship race said: “We are compassionately appealing to all Deltans to collectively support Senator James Manager and give him the mandate to become our Governor come 2023 because he is an illustrious of the soil who has learnt the ropes, cut his teeth and paid his dues.” Comrade Mike Tiemo the Good Governance Advocate stated that Senator James Manager contributed to the success and Victory of ex-governors like His Excellency, Chief Felix Ibru of blessed memory, His Excellency, Chief James Onanefe lbori, His Excellency, Chief Dr Emmanuel Uduaghan, all former Governors, and even the sitting Governor, Senator Dr Arthur Ifeanyi Okowa without any opposition. POLL Summarily, he said: “We the members of Niger Deltans Campaign For Development And Progressive Governance using the instrumentality of this medium, hereby humbly appeal to all Deltans across the three Senatorial Districts, especially to all former and present Governor, Delta State traditional rulers, the delegates, chiefs, elders, leaders, women, youths and the general public to kindly shun tribalism, segregation, zoning, and ethnocentrism to give a kind consideration to the divine request of distinguished Senator James Ebiowou Manager to become the Governor of Delta State come 2023,” he concluded.